 3→//! Supports multi-line input via Shift+Enter. Text is pre-wrapped at word
 4→//! boundaries (falls back to char boundaries when a word exceeds the width).
 5→//! Each `Line` given to ratatui represents exactly one visual row — no `.wrap()`
 6→//! is used, eliminating mismatch between cursor math and text layout.
